(66393, 80000, 6039, 1, 'A Story To Begin', '', '2013-08-10 00:00:00', 2000, 40, 0, 9, 'Now, I see the sunshine spread into the window, what a morning.\n(我看見陽光自床台灑落, 多麼美麗的早晨)\nI make a wish, Hoping all these things could be reality, not a story.\n(我默許, 希望這一切是真實的, 而非故事)\n\nI wonder why! All these lies! Why can get throught nights and nights?\n(我納悶, 為何這些謊言可以如此度過一夜又一夜)\n眼前的我們   重複了太多  那無謂的惶恐\n\nOpen the window, thought it''s broken, I would give Teddy a solar bath.\n(打開窗戶, 雖然他已殘破不堪, 我還是讓泰迪熊做了溫暖的日光浴)\nPace is approching, thought it''s scary, I will put the smile on my face.\n(我聽到那步伐接近, 盡管令人恐懼, 我依然會在臉上擺上笑容)\n\nDon''t let the mercy take over your concious.\n(別讓憐憫之心, 兌換了你的意識)\nYou''re on the way to hell.\n(你在前往地獄的路上)  \nJust stop the fear, try to rise up your anger.\n(停止你的恐懼, 試著揚起你的憤怒!)\nAnd I think it''s time to change.\n(我想是改變的時候了)             \n\nWhy can''t we believe in our decision?\n(為何我們不能相信自己的抉擇)\nWhen we lost ourselves in this situation.\n(當我們迷失在這樣的局面)\n\nHow am i get throught this? a story to begin.\n(我該如何度過, 這即將開始的故事)\n\nWhen we across the fear.\n(當我們穿越過恐懼)\nThe sorrow in my tears.\n(那在眼淚中的悲傷)\nI wake up to destroy the lies.\n(我將崛起, 只為了毀滅那些謊言)\nDestroy the lies.\n(毀滅那些謊言!)\nLet flame burns the sky.\n(讓烈焰燃燒天空)\nLet Dark erode this night.\n(讓黑暗侵蝕這個夜晚)\n\nLet flood rage in my eyes.\n(任由洪患在我眼中肆虐)\n\nI wonder why! All these lies! Why can get throught nights and nights?\n(我納悶, 為何這些謊言可以如此度過一夜又一夜)\n眼前的我們   重複了太多  那無謂的惶恐\n\n*Break Down\nWe will rise up our broken wings!!\n(我們將揚起我們殘破的翅膀)\nAnd crash this disaster!\n(然後衝擊這場戰爭)\nOne direction to figure out.\n(釐清真相的路只有一條)\nNo more nonsense would defeat my hate.\n(再也沒有廢話能擊倒我的贈恨)\n\nI ask myself why, follow the devil after?\n(我自問為什麼, 會選擇追隨身後的惡魔?)\nIt stand behind the corner,tell me the dream is over.\n(他就站在街角後, 告訴我夢已經結束了)\n\nWhen the darkness pass away...\n(當黑暗逐漸消逝)\n(we''er on the way closer to the sky!)\n(我們在更接近天空的道上!)\nBefore the tick we have to wake.\n(就在我們必須夢醒的那一刻前)\n\nTo you, to me, its cruel.\n(對你, 對我, 都是殘酷)\nSet me free, leave me behind without memory.\n(放我自由吧, 連同回憶一起將我拋在腦後)\nAnd please just walk away.\n(然後, 懇求你, 離去)', '', 248, '', 'Attack Before', '阿方 秉諺', 'Black Frequency Studio', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2013-08-26 23:15:42', '2015-03-12 14:01:55', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(66394, 80000, 6039, 2, 'Wanted', '', '2013-08-10 00:00:00', 2000, 40, 0, 9, 'They pay me, betrayal!\n(他們所回報我的, 是背叛!)\n\nI feel my tremble when I hide behind the wall.\n(躲在牆後, 我感受到自己的顫抖)\nCold air, slow breath, the sight in a trap, screaming in net.\n(冷冽的空氣, 沉緩的氣息, 在陷阱裡的視野, 網中的吶喊)\nThe way i respond,sending you, all down to hell. \n(我的回應, 是將你們全送進煉獄)\nIt''s the final revolution!\n(這將是最後的革命!)\n\nThere''s no sunrise, after this night.\n(過了今夜, 曙光不再)\nTry to feel, the sorrow in every slice \n(請試著感受, 每刀所劃下的悲傷)\n\nI know the freedom holding in my hand.\n(我知道, 那已握在我手中的自由)\nThe crush is coming, awaring, its suffocated.\n(小心, 這衝擊將使你窒息)\nI am the hater heading for this war.\n(我是一頭栽進這場戰爭的憎恨者)\nTry to stay focus, you loser. \nIm your disaster.\n(請試著專注, 你這個敗者, 我將是你的災難!)\n\nThe memory''s scratching my eyes.\n(回憶刮花了我的眼睛)\nWhen you''re trembling in my sight.\n(當你在我眼前顫抖)\nYour time has come.\n(你的時日到了)\nSo stop being numb.\n(別再麻木不仁)\nYou''ll pay for what you''ve done!\n(你將付出代價!)\nDesperation turns to violence.\n(絕望已經轉為暴力)\nWhen the war begins, the slaughter is the only way!\n(當戰爭開始, 殺戮是唯一的道路!)\n\nAnd now, its my fucking revenge yeahhhh\n(現在, 復仇時刻來了!)\nto kill them all!\n(為了殺光他們!)\n\nLets redden this night.\n(讓我們血染這個夜晚)\nAnd we''ll be free!\n(然後我們方能自由!)\nBlood will wash my guilt and yours.\n(讓血洗滌你我的罪)\n\nI! WILL! BE! STRONG! TO! SEND!\nyou down to hell!!!!!\n(為了送你下地獄, 我將更強壯)\nAND BURN------\n(在地獄被焚吧!)\nKeep in mind forever, I will be your vengeance.\n(永遠記著, 我將復仇)\nI''ll never surrender, mother fucker!\n(馬的發科我不會投降的啦!)\n', '', 239, '', 'Attack Before', '阿方 秉諺', 'Black Frequency Studio', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2013-08-26 23:20:11', '2015-03-12 14:01:55', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(66395, 80000, 6039, 3, 'Behind The Wall', '', '2013-08-10 00:00:00', 2000, 40, 0, 9, 'I know I have to cross behind the wall.\n(我知道, 我必須翻越那道牆)\nBut I still always be inside.\n(而我卻依然在牆後)\nThis time I try to find a reason for\n(這次, 我試著尋找)\nwhy i never trust my mind.\n(為什麼我總是不相信自己)\n\nWalk in deeper place again.\n(再次走到更深處)\nFeel my heartbeat bitter taste.\n(去品嚐心跳的苦澀)\nI try I cry I fall apart tonight.\n(我嘗試, 我哭泣, 並在今夜崩解)\nLonely darkness break my mind.\n(孤寂的黑敲擊著我)\nKilling me with emptiness.\n(空虛感制裁著我)\nI can''t breathe now.\n(我已經快要窒息) \n\nNo body will know what I fight for, what im searching.\nTill your heartbeat cease, I found my world''s end.\nBut I did hate you, right? I still hate you.\nThen who can tell me what am I feeling now?\nlonly? empty?....homeless\n(沒有人知道我到底為了什麼而戰, 我又在尋找什麼\n直到你的心跳停止, 我才發現我的世界末日\n但我曾經很憎恨你,不是嗎?我依然憎恨你\n那誰能告訴我, 這是什麼樣的心情?\n孤單? 空虛? 無助?)\n\nI kill myself with\nthe devil in my mind. \n(我殺了自己, 連同自己心中的魔鬼)\nI cant recover with hands of blood.\n(雙手鮮血,已經無法挽回)\n\nIt can''t be ending.\n(這不該是結局)\nI must to break my life.\n(我必須摧毀現在的生活)\nPick up your shadow, get rid of past.\n(撿起你的影子, 擺脫過去吧!)\n\nHeard the calling from the past.\n(聽到來自過去的呼喚)\nWhat im regret for?\n(而我在懊悔什麼?)\n\nTill your heart no longer beats, then I realize.\n(直到你心跳止息, 我才明白)\nTo where i go.\n(到我要去的地方)\nlife is journey you can''t leave it.\n(生命是段旅程, 你無法擺脫)\n\nTo whom I trust.\n(去相信我所信的)\nUnder secret hiding story.\n(在秘密之後總有個故事)\nYou never see me!\n(你卻從沒看到我)\n\nWalk in city. (where I should leave it behind.)\n(走在這個城市裡)(我該擺脫的地方)\nPick my pack and leave. (I pick my pack and leave.)\n(拾起行囊, 準備離去)\nTry to release(Try to release my pain) \nthe pain from the past.\n(試著釋放來自過去的痛)\nThere''s no reasons to let me stay here.\n(我已經沒有再待下去的理由)\nTouch me tonight.\nCause I will escape this life.\n(在今晚感動我, 因為我即將離開)\n\nIts time to climb over the wall x3\n(是翻過圍牆的時刻了!)\n\n\nIts the time! \n(時間到了)\nTake a breath and close your eyes and pay for sisns.\n(深呼吸, 閉起雙眼, 償還你的罪)\nGo back to when you were meant to fade out.\n(回到你應該消失的時候)\nThose are my last words.\n(這是我的遺言)\n\nI''m seeking a place\nThat I can live simply\n(我在尋找能讓我甘於平凡的地方)\nA new dream A new way.(A new faith now.)\n(一個新的夢, 新的道路)(新的自信)\n\nNow I pray for forgiveness.\n(現在 我祈求你的原諒)\nCould you stay with me?  (can u see it bleed inside.)\n(你可以繼續陪著我嗎?)(你能看見我心裡流著血嗎?)\nNow I pray for confidence.\n(現在 我祈求更多的信心)\nCould you say its fake? (can you feel i''m bleeding inside.) \n(可不可以告訴我 這不是真的?) (你能感覺到我心裡流著血嗎?)', '', 312, '', 'Attack Before', '阿方 秉諺', 'Black Frequency Studio', '迷失裂痕', '', 0, 1, 0, '2013-08-26 23:23:58', '2015-03-12 14:01:55', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
